/1526364-20200515.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526364-20200515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=56ea7b58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526364-20200515.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=80f1ac71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526364-20200515.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"擰轉頭就日日威脅臺灣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"所以佢強調1國囉，台灣係中國1部份，只係內戰緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377cb9965ce3c81387ee6fb2b28fd04bbda874b0","tid":2017662,"uid":18786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"一帶一路都已經唔知威脅咗幾多國家啦"},{"pid":"85ef394a3d2394078898e72aec7cd2a9a854d89e","tid":2017662,"uid":49161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"把口話守禮，下體在抽插"},{"pid":"eb0fe961050094450a7c36634ac962bc36b8fe4c","tid":2017662,"uid":263336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"湄公河<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b6664305d2fe19c69addd326cb4184d4e09c2c","tid":2017662,"uid":102997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"答案只會有利，不會有弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09049973d3a7661f32bd4c273e325a6493de3df2","tid":2017662,"uid":37820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"不對任何國定構成威脅<br />\n轉頭又強烈譴責，又抵制邊度邊度同埋武統台灣"},{"pid":"2310ed19bfaaae7ec4a1a56c5d34e1b469d4f7ca","tid":2017662,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:44:51.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi